title: Championship QBs Do's and Dont's
description:
Wendi Nix, Greg McElroy, and Tom Luginbill discuss the Clemson - Notre Dame rematch, what this weekend's quarterbacks need to do to be successful and what the results of these championship games could have on the College Football Playoffs.
